  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to register the precision of image fusion between live
      sonography and CT, MRI or PET/CT of liver lesions and other focal lesions in the abdomen. To
      test whether it will be possible to biopsy guided by image fusion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
